[
    {
        "content": "<p>I need to add POST transactions into a Bundle. How do I attach POST body? The only example I find is from Facebook API which attaches POST body as Base64 encoded string. Thanks.</p>",
        "id": 153874014,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488291021
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>What's the use case? (sorry, can't understand from your question)</p>",
        "id": 153874017,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1488292672
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>When using ValueSet $validate-code operation, client can use HTTP POST with body of Parameters. Here is the example from the spec:</p>",
        "id": 153874020,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488292945
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>POST [base]/ValueSet/$validate-code<br>\n[other headers]</p>\n<p>{<br>\n  \"ResourceType\" : \"Parameters\",<br>\n  \"parameter\" : [<br>\n    {<br>\n    \"name\" : \"coding\",<br>\n    \"valueCodeableConcept\" : {<br>\n      \"coding\" : {<br>\n        \"system\" : \"<a href=\"http://loinc.org\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://loinc.org\">http://loinc.org</a>\",<br>\n          \"code\" : \"1963-8\",<br>\n      \"display\" : \"test\"<br>\n      }<br>\n    }<br>\n  },<br>\n  {<br>\n    \"name\" : \"valueSet\",<br>\n    \"resource\": {<br>\n      \"resourceType\" : \"ValueSet\",<br>\n    [etc]<br>\n    }<br>\n  }<br>\n  ]<br>\n}</p>",
        "id": 153874021,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488292947
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If I want to validate several codes in one server request, I can add all requests into a Bundle, like this:</p>",
        "id": 153874023,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488293140
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>{<br>\n  \"resourceType\": \"Bundle\",<br>\n  \"type\": \"batch\",<br>\n  \"entry\": [{<br>\n    \"request\": {<br>\n      \"method\": \"POST\",<br>\n      \"url\": \"ValueSet/$validate-code\"<br>\n    }<br>\n  },<br>\n {<br>\n    \"request\": {<br>\n      \"method\": \"POST\",<br>\n      \"url\": \"ValueSet/$validate-code\"<br>\n    }<br>\n  }]<br>\n}</p>",
        "id": 153874024,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488293230
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>How do I attach Parameters body in each entry?</p>",
        "id": 153874025,
        "sender_full_name": "Yunwei Wang",
        "timestamp": 1488293258
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The Parameters instance would be inside the \"resource\" component of the entry</p>",
        "id": 153874043,
        "sender_full_name": "Lloyd McKenzie",
        "timestamp": 1488298559
    },
